    "The model comprises three primary modules:",
    "The first module is the interactive text semantic feature module.",
    "It employs the multihead self-attention mechanism to calculate and merge the source tweets or microblogs with comments and repost content.",
    "This process generates a new feature to represent each source post or event. 2.",
    "The second module is the anti-interference propagation structure feature module."
